01:09:22,620 --> 01:09:24,690
它们对肉体伤害才有反应
We designed them to respond to physical damage.

590
01:09:24,690 --> 01:09:27,180
精神伤害也会引起生理反应
Emotional damage can manifest physically.

591
01:09:28,930 --> 01:09:30,480
像是什么?
Like what?

592
01:09:34,560 --> 01:09:36,430
严重的心理创伤
Serious trauma.

593
01:09:38,600 --> 01:09:40,430
被压抑的记忆
Repressed memories.

594
01:09:45,810 --> 01:09:51,010
你爸逼问我小时候发生的事
Your father grilled me about something that happened to me from early childhood...

595
01:09:51,010 --> 01:09:52,980
他说我应该记得
that I'm supposed to remember.

596
01:09:53,380 --> 01:09:54,620
是吗?
He did?

597
01:09:54,620 --> 01:09:56,410
听起来很严重
It sounded bad, but...

598
01:09:57,690 --> 01:10:00,120
但是我真的不记得
I honestly don't remember.

599
01:10:02,960 --> 01:10:04,820
我最担心的是
The thing that worries me...

600
01:10:07,700 --> 01:10:09,820
肉体伤害有限
a physical wound is finite,

601
01:10:10,600 --> 01:10:15,200
精神伤害却是难以衡量
but with emotions,

602
01:10:15,740 --> 01:10:17,710
很可能引起连锁反应
what's to say it won't just go on and on and start a chain reaction?

603
01:10:21,540 --> 01:10:23,940
你知道我最害怕什么吗?
You know what scares me the most?

604
01:10:26,020 --> 01:10:27,810
当我开始改变
When it happens,when it comes over me…

605
01:10:29,150 --> 01:10:33,490
当我无法抗拒、完全失去控制
and I totally lose control,

606
01:10:35,930 --> 01:10:37,550
我喜欢那种感觉
I like it.

607
01:10:55,110 --> 01:10:58,270
我抱住你了  对不起
It's okay. I got you. I'm sorry.

608
01:10:59,320 --> 01:11:01,810
你没事  这只是麻醉枪
You'll be okay. It's just to make you sleep.

609
01:11:01,820 --> 01:11:02,990
目标倒下
Target down.

610
01:11:02,990 --> 01:11:04,480
目标被捕
Target secure.

611
01:11:04,820 --> 01:11:07,650
我要带你到安全地方
I'm going to take you someplace safe.Okay? Bruce?

612
01:14:00,000 --> 01:14:01,200
立正
Clear!Attention on deck.

613
01:14:01,200 --> 01:14:02,570
继续吧
Carry on.

614
01:14:11,680 --> 01:14:14,050
他被我们埋在地底深处
We're buried out here in the middle of nowhere.

615
01:14:14,050 --> 01:14:16,250
你打算把他关多久?
How long are you gonna keep him sedated?

616
01:14:16,250 --> 01:14:18,590
有必要关一辈子
For the rest of his natural life, if I have to.

617
01:14:18,590 --> 01:14:20,420
你说我可以相信你
You said I could trust you.

618
01:14:20,420 --> 01:14:22,020
我是你父亲
I'm your father.

619
01:14:22,060 --> 01:14:24,730
我会做我认为是对的事
You can trust me to do what I think is right,

620
01:14:24,730 --> 01:14:26,400
而不是你要我做的事
not what you think you want.

621
01:14:26,400 --> 01:14:27,560
他是个人
He is a human being.

622
01:14:27,560 --> 01:14:29,960
他也是别的东西
He is also something else.

623
01:14:30,230 --> 01:14:31,960
假如他逃出去
Suppose he gets out,

624
01:14:32,140 --> 01:14:35,470
在大城市发飙怎么办?
has one of his little mood swings in a populated area.

625
01:14:35,470 --> 01:14:37,740
我知道他很危险
Yes, I'm aware of the potential danger.

626
01:14:37,740 --> 01:14:39,880
但是他也救了我一命
I'm also aware that he saved my life.

627
01:14:39,880 --> 01:14:42,570
他替你痛宰一只变种贵宝狗
Yeah, from a mutant French poodle.

628
01:14:43,050 --> 01:14:45,210
我真该对他感激涕零
I'm indebted to him for that.

629
01:14:45,420 --> 01:14:47,480
他也把三个人打伤
He also put three men in a hospital,

630
01:14:47,480 --> 01:14:50,020
陶柏也瘸了腿  你要我怎样?
and Talbot's barely walking! What do you want me to do?

631
01:14:50,020 --> 01:14:51,950
我要你帮助他
I want you to help him!

632
01:14:53,290 --> 01:14:55,160
你为什么这么怕他?
Why is He such a threat to you?

633
01:14:55,160 --> 01:14:57,290
我了解他的出身
Because I know what He comes from.

634
01:14:57,290 --> 01:15:01,900
他身上每一个分子都跟他爸一样
He is his father's son, every last molecule of him.

635
01:15:01,900 --> 01:15:04,060
他说他不认识他爸
He says he doesn't know his father,

636
01:15:04,230 --> 01:15:09,170
但是他们却进行相同的研究
but he's workin'in the same exact goddamn field his father did.

637
01:15:09,840 --> 01:15:13,110
如果他不是说谎那就更可怕
So either he's lyin'... or it's somethin' worse, 

638
01:15:13,110 --> 01:15:14,140
因为他…
and he's...

639
01:15:14,140 --> 01:15:15,610
怎么样?
What?

640
01:15:16,050 --> 01:15:19,310
命中注定追随他父亲的脚步?
Predestined to follow in his father's footsteps?

641
01:15:21,450 --> 01:15:23,480
我本来想说他受了诅咒
I was gonna say "damned."

642
01:15:25,020 --> 01:15:26,750
当然了
Of course you were.

643
01:15:27,160 --> 01:15:29,720
身为科学家我相信
But I'm a scientist.

644
01:15:29,890 --> 01:15:33,230
我能找出原因帮助他
As a scientist, I believe we can figure this out and he can be helped.

645
01:15:33,460 --> 01:15:35,190
我知道
I know you do.

646
01:15:36,700 --> 01:15:40,070
不管你怎么想
Look, whether you know or care,

647
01:15:40,970 --> 01:15:43,770
我都为你所做的感到自豪
I've got a lot of pride in what you've done.

648
01:15:44,510 --> 01:15:46,910
但这件事太危险了
But this is too big for you.

649
01:15:46,910 --> 01:15:50,640
我知道政府想利用他当武器
Look, I know the government thinks they have a weapon on their hands.

650
01:15:51,150 --> 01:15:53,450
要不然他早就死了
Otherwise, he'd be dead by now.

651
01:15:53,450 --> 01:15:55,690
他们大可以对他为所欲为
They can probe and prod all they want,

652
01:15:55,690 --> 01:15:57,920
但是也让我帮助他
and in the meanwhile, just let me try to help him.

653
01:15:57,920 --> 01:16:00,320
没有人比我更了解他
Nobody knows him better than I do.

654
01:16:04,330 --> 01:16:06,420
大卫班纳对他做了什么?
What did David Banner do to him?

655
01:16:11,200 --> 01:16:12,690
掩护左翼
Cover left! Clear left.

656
01:16:13,140 --> 01:16:14,620
掩护右翼
Cover right!

657
01:18:25,770 --> 01:18:27,460
你在干什么?
What's happening here?

658
01:18:28,770 --> 01:18:30,200
我的手
My hand.

659
01:18:32,440 --> 01:18:36,000
我儿子DNA的力量
You see, the strength of my son's DNA...

660
01:18:37,510 --> 01:18:41,970
结合奈米微生物的再生能力
combined with nanomed reconstruction...

661
01:18:43,820 --> 01:18:47,760
让我能溶入任何物体的本质
You see, I can partake with the essences of all things.

662
01:18:49,590 --> 01:18:54,390
请你把手举起来
Gonna have to ask you to put your hands up, pal, okay?

663
01:18:55,400 --> 01:18:57,200
慢慢来
Nice and easy.

664
01:19:03,670 --> 01:19:08,840
你真以为我们是分开的吗?
Do you really believe that I am separate from you?

665
01:19:27,530 --> 01:19:29,050
我在哪里?
Where am I?

666
01:19:33,600 --> 01:19:35,090
你回家了
You're home.

667
01:19:47,980 --> 01:19:50,420
不敢相信我们住过这儿
It's hard to believe we used to live here.

668
01:19:53,260 --> 01:19:56,320
我一定见过你  甚至认识你
I must have seen you or known you.

669
01:19:56,660 --> 01:19:58,680
真希望我记得起来
If only I could remember.

670
01:21:15,300 --> 01:21:16,670
走吧
Let's go.

671
01:21:18,340 --> 01:21:20,030
试着回想一下
Please try.

672
01:22:14,340 --> 01:22:15,820
怎么了?
What is it?

673
01:22:16,600 --> 01:22:18,070
没什么
Nothing.

674
01:22:19,310 --> 01:22:20,800
真的吗?
Really?

675
01:22:23,880 --> 01:22:25,240
该死
Damn it.

676
01:22:30,390 --> 01:22:31,820
好吧
Okay, Betty...

677
01:22:33,050 --> 01:22:34,820
你想知道什么?
what do you want to know?

678
01:22:37,790 --> 01:22:39,730
那间房间有什么?
What was in that room?

679
01:22:50,770 --> 01:22:52,670
你怕我会看到什么?
What are you afraid that I'll see?

680
01:22:59,350 --> 01:23:02,540
瞧  什么也没有
See? There's nothing.

681
01:23:04,050 --> 01:23:05,540
空无一物
It's empty.

682
01:23:18,430 --> 01:23:20,700
我为什么不能见他?
What do you mean, I don't have access to him?

683
01:23:20,700 --> 01:23:25,540
国安局决定把这个威胁
NSA has decided to turn over study of the, uh...

684
01:23:25,540 --> 01:23:27,230
交给亚矽公司
the threat to Atheon.

685
01:23:27,840 --> 01:23:31,750
你是基地指挥官  你能作主
But you're head of the base.I thought you were in charge.

686
01:23:31,750 --> 01:23:35,680
我做不了决策  只能服从命令
But I don't set policy, and I still take orders.

687
01:23:38,550 --> 01:23:41,680
我不敢相信陶柏竟然出卖我
I can't believe Talbot would go around me like this!

688
01:23:43,890 --> 01:23:47,720
很多有权有势的人都想插一脚
Oh, there's a lot of powerful people that want in on this.

689
01:23:48,000 --> 01:23:50,930
他们可以赚很多钱
And money to be made... lots of it.

690
01:23:56,440 --> 01:23:58,560
你知道最糟的是什么吗?
You know the worst part about all this?

691
01:23:59,640 --> 01:24:02,580
当我把父亲关起来把儿子送走
When I had David Banner locked up and sent that kid away,

692
01:24:02,580 --> 01:24:05,410
我只把他当成一般受害者
I didn't give that boy a second thought; he was just collateral damage.

693
01:24:07,080 --> 01:24:09,210
他不再是了吧!
Well, he isn't anymore, is he?

694
01:24:12,650 --> 01:24:14,350
我该怎么做?
What can I do?

695
01:24:16,220 --> 01:24:18,190
你该回家了
You can go home now.

696
01:24:19,930 --> 01:24:22,230
我很想让你跟他道别
I'd tell you to go and say good-bye, but I've already been informed...

697
01:24:22,230 --> 01:24:27,360
但是我奉命不准他和外界联系
that for now all further contact is out of the question.

698
01:24:28,340 --> 01:24:29,700
是啊
Hiya,

699
01:25:08,110 --> 01:25:10,340
布鲁斯  你好吗?
Bruce. How ya feelin'?

700
01:25:10,610 --> 01:25:12,510
这儿的饭好不好吃?
Grub okay in here for ya?

701
01:25:13,780 --> 01:25:15,340
你要什么?
What do you want?

702
01:25:15,380 --> 01:25:17,040
问得好
That's a good question.

703
01:25:17,850 --> 01:25:21,750
我需要你的细胞触发化学反应
See, I need your cells to trigger some chemical distress signals.

704
01:25:22,320 --> 01:25:25,420
把你变成那个绿巨人
You know, so you can turn a little green for me again...

705
01:25:26,030 --> 01:25:29,260
让我把真正的你大卸八块
and I can carve off a piece of the real you,

706
01:25:29,600 --> 01:25:33,070
分析后申请专利赚大钱
analyze it, patent it, make a fortune.

707
01:25:33,600 --> 01:25:35,160
你不介意吧?
Do you mind?

708
01:25:36,340 --> 01:25:38,100
我不会让你得逞
I'll never let you.

709
01:25:38,910 --> 01:25:41,200
你别无选择
I'm not sure you've got much of a choice.

710
01:25:43,380 --> 01:25:46,780
你不生气吗?
Come on, Bruce. Aren't you feeling a little angry?

711
01:25:46,780 --> 01:25:50,580
贝蒂弃你不顾  只有我陪你玩
After all, you've only got me to play with now that Betty's dumped you and gone back to Berkeley.

712
01:25:51,220 --> 01:25:52,520
你在说谎
You're lying.

713
01:25:52,520 --> 01:25:55,220
这是双赢的局面
You know, for me this is a win-win situation.

714
01:25:55,220 --> 01:25:57,960
你变成绿巨人乖乖等死
You turn green, and all these guys come in and kill you...

715
01:25:57,960 --> 01:25:59,560
让我进行解剖
and I perform the autopsy.

716
01:25:59,560 --> 01:26:01,050
不然的话
- You don't...

717
01:26:03,030 --> 01:26:07,260
我就海扁你一顿  掐断你脖子
And I mop the floor with you and maybe by accident go too far and break your neck.

718
01:26:07,440 --> 01:26:09,330
这很不科学
Bad science, maybe...

719
01:26:10,440 --> 01:26:12,170
但是却让我很爽
but personally gratifying.

720
01:26:14,210 --> 01:26:18,040
来呀  看你有什么能耐
Come on, Bruce! Let's see what you got.

721
01:26:19,350 --> 01:26:20,640
不要
Never.

722
01:26:26,720 --> 01:26:28,980
你也许能用意志力控制
but subconsciously,

723
01:26:29,720 --> 01:26:32,590
但是你却控制不了潜意识
I bet that's another story.

724
01:27:02,820 --> 01:27:05,450
刺激他的脑波吧
All right, let's jump-start those brain waves.

725
01:27:32,720 --> 01:27:36,320
亲爱的罗小姐  欢迎回家
My dear Miss Ross. Welcome back.

726
01:27:37,130 --> 01:27:39,390
外面有两名守卫
There are two guards right outside.

727
01:27:39,400 --> 01:27:44,767
别担心，我已经不再生你的气了
You don't have to worry. I'm not angry with you. Not anymore.

728
01:27:42,730 --> 01:27:44,390


729
01:27:45,570 --> 01:27:47,070
你要什么?
What do you want?

730
01:27:47,070 --> 01:27:50,230
我这一生已经完了
It's over for me now. I know that.

731
01:27:50,510 --> 01:27:52,940
布鲁斯也快完了
And soon it'll be over for Bruce.

732
01:27:54,780 --> 01:27:56,610
所以我才来找你
That's why I've come to you...

733
01:27:56,610 --> 01:28:00,770
请你说服你父亲
to ask you if you could persuade your father,

734
01:28:00,920 --> 01:28:03,510
请他以一个父亲的角度考虑
as a man, as a father himself,

735
01:28:04,790 --> 01:28:08,720
我愿意乖乖自首
that if I turn myself in now, peacefully...

736
01:28:08,720 --> 01:28:10,820
在他把我关一辈子之前
and before he puts me away forever,

737
01:28:11,890 --> 01:28:16,990
请他让我见我儿子最后一面
that he would let me see my son for one last time.

738
01:28:17,830 --> 01:28:19,730
你能帮我这个忙吗?
Could you do that for me?

739
01:28:23,240 --> 01:28:25,370
现在我爸也不能作主
It's out of my father's hands now.

740
01:28:30,380 --> 01:28:34,080
我明白  他也成为傀儡
I understand. He's a puppet now.

741
01:28:35,058 --> 01:28:37,322
-我不会怪他   -你也不应该
-I don't blame him.  -You shouldn't.


742
01:28:37,394 --> 01:28:41,160
你应该对你儿子做的事情感到愧疚
You should blame yourself for what you've done to your son.




744
01:28:42,200 --> 01:28:44,790
罗小姐，我对我儿子做什么了？
And what have I done to my son, Miss Ross?

745
01:28:44,790 --> 01:28:45,990
什么也没做
Nothing.

746
01:28:45,990 --> 01:28:50,060
我只不过尽力想改善我自己
I tried to improve on the limits in myself.

747
01:28:50,330 --> 01:28:52,770
是我自己  不是他
Myself!  Not him!

748
01:28:53,170 --> 01:28:54,860
你能了解吗?
Can you understand?

749
01:28:55,040 --> 01:28:56,590
违反自然定律
To improve on nature.

750
01:28:56,591 --> 01:28:59,370
我的自然本质，对自己的认知
My nature!  Knowledge of oneself!

751
01:28:59,370 --> 01:29:02,078
这是追求真理唯一的道路
It's the only path to the truth...

752
01:29:02,079 --> 01:29:06,950
让人类挣脱上帝的束缚
that give men the power to go beyond God's boundaries!

753
01:29:07,480 --> 01:29:11,420
但是你不能为了自己牺牲别人
You know what's beyond your boundaries? Other people.

754
01:29:12,490 --> 01:29:15,150
你只为布鲁斯带来恐惧
All you've given Bruce is fear.

755
01:29:17,230 --> 01:29:18,950
对生命的恐惧
Fear of life.

756
01:29:22,200 --> 01:29:23,630
恐惧?
Fear?

757
01:29:25,330 --> 01:29:27,600
也许吧
Perhaps, Miss Ross.

758
01:29:29,540 --> 01:29:31,700
还有孤独
And loneliness too.

759
01:29:35,440 --> 01:29:37,470
两者我都经历过
Yes... I feel them both.

760
01:29:40,420 --> 01:29:45,350
但是我也曾拥有幸福
But I have lived... completely once.

761
01:29:47,360 --> 01:29:49,720
我深爱我的妻子
I was so much in love,

762
01:29:50,530 --> 01:29:53,490
她也很想要一个小孩
and she so much wanted a baby.

763
01:29:53,500 --> 01:29:55,220
我的小孩
My baby.

764
01:30:02,870 --> 01:30:05,970
她一怀孕我就知道
I could tell from the moment she conceived...

765
01:30:05,970 --> 01:30:10,640
那不是个儿子  是别的东西
that it wasn't a son I had given her but something else.

766
01:30:11,450 --> 01:30:13,480
也许是一个怪物
A monster, maybe.

767
01:30:13,480 --> 01:30:16,350
我早该结束他的生命
I should have put a stop to it right then,

768
01:30:16,450 --> 01:30:18,280
但是我很好奇
but I was curious

769
01:30:18,790 --> 01:30:20,910
那也是我的沉沦
and that was my downfall.

770
01:30:21,560 --> 01:30:25,230
当我看着小生命逐渐成长
And as I watched this tiny life unfold,

771
01:30:25,230 --> 01:30:28,390
就想到他长大后会有多痛苦
I began to imagine the horror of it,

772
01:30:29,000 --> 01:30:35,200
我的好奇心被慈悲心取代
and my curiosity was replaced with compassion.

773
01:30:37,910 --> 01:30:40,440
但是他们不让我治好他
But they took away my chance to cure him.

774
01:30:40,440 --> 01:30:42,880
你父亲把我关起来
Your father threw me out.

775
01:30:44,280 --> 01:30:46,850
那一天我记得很清楚
what are you doing?   I remember that day so well...

776
01:30:46,850 --> 01:30:49,580
每一刻、每一种感觉
every moment, every sensation...

777
01:30:49,580 --> 01:30:51,620
我走进屋子
walking into the house,

778
01:30:51,620 --> 01:30:55,110
手里拿着刀的触感
the feeling of the handle of the knife in my hand.

779
01:30:55,120 --> 01:31:00,460
