David, no! Talk to me! Listen!

782
01:31:06,730 --> 01:31:09,100
但是她让我吓一跳
But then she surprised me.

783
01:31:15,740 --> 01:31:21,480
好像…   她和那把刀
It was as if..    she and the knife...

784
01:31:22,180 --> 01:31:23,620
合而为一
merged.

785
01:31:33,390 --> 01:31:34,860
不
No!

786
01:31:34,960 --> 01:31:41,890
你无法想像我有多绝望
You cannot imagine the unbearable finality of it.

787
01:31:42,840 --> 01:31:44,770
就在那一瞬间
And in that one moment...

788
01:31:45,540 --> 01:31:49,240
我夺走我所爱的一切
I took everything that was dear to me...

789
01:31:49,940 --> 01:31:56,250
心中一片空虚  剩下痛苦回忆
and transformed it into nothing more than a memory.

790
01:32:11,530 --> 01:32:15,030
太好了  他做了可怕的噩梦
Bingo! That must be some jumbo nightmare he just had.

791
01:32:19,610 --> 01:32:21,800
