刺不进去
Sir, negative on drill penetration.

793
01:32:29,250 --> 01:32:31,420
那就用力  使用全力
Damn it, drill him harder! Give him full RPMs.

794
01:32:31,420 --> 01:32:33,350
加油
Come on, Holeman! Come on!

795
01:32:47,200 --> 01:32:48,540
杀了他吗?
Should I neutralize?

796
01:32:48,540 --> 01:32:50,940
不  杀了他就没用
No! I can't do anything with goop! Come on!

797
01:33:04,320 --> 01:33:06,080
把他麻醉
All right, put him to sleep.

798
01:33:16,230 --> 01:33:17,920
一点都没有用
It's not stopping him!

799
