派出我们的危机小组
Ready room, send in our containment team.

800
01:33:27,140 --> 01:33:28,740
使用非致命武器
Non-lethals only. I repeat, non-lethals only.

801
01:33:28,740 --> 01:33:32,080
我一定要采到他的样本
I must have a sample of him.

802
01:33:32,250 --> 01:33:33,610
长官
Sir!

803
01:33:36,150 --> 01:33:37,580
天啊
Jesus!

804
01:33:38,250 --> 01:33:39,420
用泡沫喷他
Hit him with the foam.

805
01:33:39,420 --> 01:33:41,110
强力化学泡沫
Deploy containment foam.

806
01:33:42,460 --> 01:33:44,150
陶柏  快回答
Talbot, talk to me.

807
