Cease fire! Under control, General. I'll let you know if we need you.

808
01:33:49,430 --> 01:33:52,100
不行  我要你马上离开
Unacceptable. Unseat your asses down here immediately.

809
01:33:52,100 --> 01:33:55,200
全员撤退  终止你的行动
I want a full-court evacuation now.

810
01:33:55,200 --> 01:33:56,640
全面封锁
I'm shutting you down. Lockdown.

811
01:33:56,640 --> 01:33:58,210
你没听到将军的话?
Didn't you hear what the general said?

812
01:33:58,210 --> 01:34:00,070
我说全面封锁
I said lockdown!

813
01:34:02,580 --> 01:34:05,310
让开  我要他的样本
Clear! I need a sample of him!

814
01:34:07,350 --> 01:34:10,440
放轻松  老兄
Take it easy there, buddy.

815
01:34:10,950 --> 01:34:13,580
这可能会有点痛
This might give you a bit of a sting here, Bruce.

816
01:34:26,700 --> 01:34:28,440
退后!
Fall back! Fall back! Clear your weapon! Clear it!

817
01:34:28,440 --> 01:34:31,310
退下去  给我M2弹
Give me the M2. 

818
01:34:31,310 --> 01:34:33,430
永别了  大家伙
So long, big boy.  

819
01:34:45,920 --> 01:34:49,150
立刻全面封锁
Lockdown the entire facility immediately.

820
01:34:51,130 --> 01:34:53,260
全面封锁

821
