探戈四号被打落
Tango Four is down.

853
01:43:42,590 --> 01:43:44,890
派出搜救小组
Have C-SAR respond to our 20 ASAP.

854
01:43:46,190 --> 01:43:48,900
快把他引开
We're okay, but, damn it, get him off us before he tears us apart!

855
01:43:48,900 --> 01:43:51,860
我打不到他  你能瞄准吗?
I've got no shot. Do you have a clear line of fire?

856
01:43:52,770 --> 01:43:53,970
小心
Watch it, Tango Flight.

857
01:43:53,970 --> 01:43:56,270
快向左飞
Break left! Break left!

858
01:43:57,910 --> 01:44:00,470
我要发射地狱火飞弹
Tango Three, pull back and set up for a Hellfire shot.

859
01:44:00,470 --> 01:44:02,910
等我们把他引开再发射
Hold your fire till we draw him off.

860
01:44:03,310 --> 01:44:05,480
探戈一号准备开火
Tango One is hot. Gun wazzed.

861
01:44:05,480 --> 01:44:07,640
收到  准备发射
Roger. Going hot. Guns ready.

862
01:44:13,150 --> 01:44:14,880
发射飞弹
Engage at will.

863
01:44:35,480 --> 01:44:37,970
退后  让我发射
Tango One, pull back! Clear my line!

864
01:44:38,510 --> 01:44:41,640
让开  我瞄准目标了
Tango Flight, clear back.

865
01:44:44,120 --> 01:44:46,710
好了  开火吧
Tango One, Tango Three. I have contact.

866
01:45:05,070 --> 01:45:08,010
我射中他了
I've got him painted for Hellfire.

867
01:45:08,080 --> 01:45:10,340
天啊  他接到我的飞弹
Holy shit! He's got my missile!

868
01:45:12,480 --> 01:45:14,380
求救!
Mayday! Mayday!

869
01:45:16,780 --> 01:45:20,150
求救  我被击落了
Mayday! Mayday! We're hit! We're going down!

870
01:45:23,720 --> 01:45:25,590
有没有人伤亡?
Give me a head count.Tango Three, give me a sit rep.

871
