直升机被击落  无人伤亡
Our kite's busted up, but we're okay.

872
01:45:33,470 --> 01:45:36,440
你们看到目标吗?
Tango Flight, do you have eyes on the target?

873
01:45:36,800 --> 01:45:39,010
他在岩石堆
Tango One. I have him in the rocks.

874
01:45:39,010 --> 01:45:41,840
全力开火  把它移为平地
Salvo all. Turn it into a parking lot.

875
01:46:02,600 --> 01:46:04,960
它被移为平地了
T-bolt, your parking lot is ready.

876
01:46:05,070 --> 01:46:08,030
油量不够  返回基地
We're bingo for fuel and ammo. R. T.B.

877
01:46:35,460 --> 01:46:39,530
指挥官  目标没被摧毁
T-bolt, this is Goodman Control.Be advised, target not destroyed.

878
01:46:39,530 --> 01:46:41,130
他又在移动
He's on the move again.

879
01:46:41,270 --> 01:46:42,630
可恶
Damn!

880
01:46:42,900 --> 01:46:44,340
找到他了
I've got it.

881
01:46:45,310 --> 01:46:47,600
看来他要回家
It appears he's heading home.

882
01:46:48,340 --> 01:46:52,510
出动战机  拦截目标
Launch fast movers.Have them intercept and engage.

883
01:46:55,880 --> 01:46:58,290
布鲁斯逃出来了
Betty, Bruce got out.

884
01:46:58,290 --> 01:47:01,310
他往你那儿去  大概是去找你
He's headed your way and probably right for you.

885
01:47:01,560 --> 01:47:03,320
你离基地多远?
How far from the base are you?

886
01:47:03,320 --> 01:47:06,520
我到了  他们把他爸带来
I'm already here. They're taking his father in now.

887
01:47:06,990 --> 01:47:10,620
这是好消息  待在那儿 贝蒂
That's all good news. Stay there, Betty.

888
01:47:11,100 --> 01:47:13,570
旧金山柏克莱

889
01:47:24,680 --> 01:47:28,050
传奇一号和二号急速接近中
Legend One rolling in hot. Legend Two breaking off left.

890
01:47:28,050 --> 01:47:30,980
我要折回来进行攻击
I think I can come back around for a gun attack.

891
01:47:31,550 --> 01:47:34,820
瞄准目标就开火
Acquire a clear target. Fire at will.

892
01:47:39,390 --> 01:47:42,020
是民航机  快爬升
Increase altitude. Civilian aircraft in vicinity.

893
01:47:47,530 --> 01:47:50,400
快拉高  你会撞到大桥
Pull up! Pull up! You're headed for the bridge!

894
