我拉不高
I can't pull up! I can't pull up!

895
01:48:03,120 --> 01:48:06,150
把他载到大气层外
Okay, you've got him now. Take him on a ride to the top of the world.

896
01:48:06,150 --> 01:48:08,420
让他吸不到空气
Let's see what the thin air will do for him.

897
01:48:09,920 --> 01:48:11,820
启动后燃引擎
Initiating afterburner.

898
01:48:29,240 --> 01:48:31,510
爬升到六万英尺高度
I'm passing flight level 600.

899
01:48:31,510 --> 01:48:33,480
我到了极限
This is out of my envelope.

900
01:48:33,810 --> 01:48:35,450
撑着点
Hang in there, Legend.

901
01:48:35,450 --> 01:48:38,650
他抓得太紧  无法维持高度
I can't maintain. He's all over my aerodynamics.

902
01:48:38,650 --> 01:48:41,090
他会比你先昏过去
He'll lose consciousness before you.

903
01:48:44,730 --> 01:48:46,420
九万五千英尺
Nine-fifty.

904
01:48:46,730 --> 01:48:50,200
我撑不下去了  我要下降
I can't hold it. I'm pulling back!

905
01:49:37,140 --> 01:49:39,310
卑微的人类
Puny human.

906
01:49:47,850 --> 01:49:51,550
他坠入大海  准备开火
Contact. He's in the water. All units, weapons hot.

907
01:49:51,560 --> 01:49:56,360
不能冒险  全力开火
Let's not take any chances.You are cleared to fire on target, Legend.

908
01:50:21,560 --> 01:50:24,830
我别无选择  一定要消灭他
Dad? Betty?We don't have a choice.I have to destroy him.

909
01:50:24,830 --> 01:50:26,260
你不能这么做
But you can't.

910
01:50:26,260 --> 01:50:29,560
把他激怒只会让他更强壮
You will only fuel his rage, and you will make him stronger.

911
01:50:30,730 --> 01:50:33,360
他是去找你的
It's you he's coming for. You know that.

912
01:50:35,300 --> 01:50:37,100
那就让我去找他
Then let me go to him.

913
01:50:38,070 --> 01:50:39,440
求求你
Please.

914
01:50:41,440 --> 01:50:43,670
给他机会冷静下来
Just give him a chance to calm down.

915
01:51:03,230 --> 01:51:08,440
旧金山领空的民航机
All aircraft vicinity of San Francisco, this is T-bolt on guard.

