Saw her face.

943
01:59:10,380 --> 01:59:11,910
棕发
Brown hair.

944
01:59:13,750 --> 01:59:15,280
棕眼
Brown eyes.

945
01:59:16,720 --> 01:59:18,450
她对我笑
She smiled at me.

946
01:59:19,790 --> 01:59:22,420
低下头亲我的脸颊
She reached down and kissed my cheek.

947
01:59:24,460 --> 01:59:26,860
